mmand run 3 times (initial, after adding test, to extract line)\n31\t\n32\t### 1-3-workflow-state-module — code-review (2026-04-02T10:55)\n33\t\n34\t- **HIGH:** `readState`/`writeState` naming collision with `state.ts` — renamed to `readWorkflowState`/`writeWorkflowState`. Fixed.\n35\t- **MEDIUM:** `isValidWorkflowState` did not validate `tasks_completed` element shapes. Fixed.\n36\t- **MEDIUM:** `isValidWorkflowState` did not validate `evaluator_scores` or `score_history` element types. Fixed.\n37\t- **MEDIUM:** No tests for array element validation edge cases. Added 6 tests. Fixed.\n38\t- **LOW (not fixed):** Branch coverage at 72.22%, stale AGENTS.md entries from stories 1-1/1-2.\n39\t- **Coverage:** 96.6% overall, all 148 files above 80% floor.\n40\t\n41\t## Token Report\n42\t- Total tool calls: 24\n43\t- By tool: Bash: 11, Read: 7, Edit: 10, Grep: 1, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n44\t- Largest Bash outputs: `npx vitest run` full suite (~10 lines), `git diff teardown.test.ts` (~50 lines)\n45\t- Files read: 9 unique, 9 total reads\n46\t- Redundant operations: 3 consecutive grep attempts for coverage data\n47\t\n48\t### 1-3-workflow-state-module — verification (2026-04-02T11:03)\n49\t\n50\t- **Verification gaps:** AC3 cross-process persistence tested via separate function calls, not actual separate OS processes\n51\t- **Coverage nuance:** Branch coverage 73.52% below 80%, but statement coverage at 80% meets AC requirement\n52\t- **Warnings:** \"Showboat not installed\" and \"No exec-plan found\" are non-blocking\n53\t- **Observation:** Clean implementation — 151 lines source, 392 lines tests\n54\t\n55\t## Token Report\n56\t- Total tool calls: 14\n57\t- By tool: Bash: 9, Read: 3, Write: 1\n58\t- Largest Bash outputs: `npm run test:unit` (~30 lines), `ls verification/` (~100 lines)\n59\t- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n60\t- Redundant operations: Ran codeharness verify twice, multiple ANSI-stripping attempts for coverage\n61\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"