non-blocking","-- **Observation:** Clean implementation — 151 lines source, 392 lines tests","-","-## Token Report","-- Total tool calls: 14","-- By tool: Bash: 9, Read: 3, Write: 1","-- Largest Bash outputs: `npm run test:unit` (~30 lines), `ls verification/` (~100 lines)","-- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads","-- Redundant operations: Ran codeharness verify twice, multiple ANSI-stripping attempts for coverage"]}],"originalFile":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-02\n\n### 1-3-workflow-state-module — create-story (2026-04-02T10:42)\n\n- **Problem:** workflow.yaml vs workflow.md naming inconsistency in skill trigger\n- **Problem:** No `_bmad/bmm/config.yaml` or `project-context.md` found — inferred from existing artifacts\n- **Workaround:** Skipped sprint-status.yaml update per orchestrator instructions\n- **Risk:** AC #3 \"state survives process exit\" is test-provable but weaker than actual process restart test\n- **Observation:** Existing state.ts uses markdown-wrapped YAML; new workflow-state uses plain YAML (intentional per architecture-v2.md)\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 16\n- By tool: Bash: 5, Read: 9, Grep: 2, Glob: 4, Write: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `ls implementation-artifacts/` (~170 lines), `ls src/lib/` (~27 lines)\n- Files read: 10 unique, 10 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n\n### 1-3-workflow-state-module — dev-story (2026-04-02T10:48)\n\n- **Problem:** Initial implementation missed `// IGNORE:` comments on catch blocks — project enforces this via boundaries test\n- **Problem:** `commands/__tests__/query.test.ts` flaky (pre-existing, unrelated)\n- **Code quality:** Branch coverage at 72.22% — uncovered branches are internal validation paths in `isValidWorkflowState()` that are hard to trigger through public API\n- **Observation:** Module is self-contained with zero internal dependencies (only output.ts for warn())\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 20\n- By tool: Bash: 8, Read: 7, Edit: 4, Grep: 0, Write: 2, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npx vitest run --coverage` (~140 lines), `npx vitest run` full suite (~10 lines)\n- Files read: 9 unique, 10 total reads\n- Redundant operations: Coverage command run 3 times (initial, after adding test, to extract line)\n\n### 1-3-workflow-state-module — code-review (2026-04-02T10:55)\n\n- **HIGH:** `readState`/`writeState` naming collision with `state.ts` — renamed to `readWorkflowState`/`writeWorkflowState`. Fixed.\n- **MEDIUM:** `isValidWorkflowState` did not validate `tasks_completed` element shapes. Fixed.\n- **MEDIUM:** `isValidWorkflowState` did not validate `evaluator_scores` or `score_history` element types. Fixed.\n- **MEDIUM:** No tests for array element validation edge cases. Added 6 tests. Fixed.\n- **LOW (not fixed):** Branch coverage at 72.22%, stale AGENTS.md entries from stories 1-1/1-2.\n- **Coverage:** 96.6% overall, all 148 files above 80% floor.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 24\n- By tool: Bash: 11, Read: 7, Edit: 10, Grep: 1, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npx vitest run` full suite (~10 lines), `git diff teardown.test.ts` (~50 lines)\n- Files read: 9 unique, 9 total reads\n- Redundant operations: 3 consecutive grep attempts for coverage data\n\n### 1-3-workflow-state-module — verification (2026-04-02T11:03)\n\n- **Verification gaps:** AC3 cross-process persistence tested via separate function calls, not actual separate OS processes\n- **Coverage nuance:** Branch coverage 73.52% below 80%, but statement coverage at 80% meets AC requirement\n- **Warnings:** \"Showboat not installed\" and \"No exec-plan found\" are non-blocking\n- **Observation:** Clean implementation — 151 lines source, 392 lines tests\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 14\n- By tool: Bash: 9, Read: 3, Write: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npm run test:unit` (~30 lines), `ls verification/` (~100 lines)\n- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n- Redundant operations: Ran codeharness verify twice, multiple ANSI-stripping attempts for coverage\n"}}
