{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01UjFBMyVEBkQyth3asESgHE","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Story 2.1: Workflow YAML JSON Schema\n2\t\n3\tStatus: ready-for-dev\n4\t\n5\t## Story\n6\t\n7\tAs a developer,\n8\tI want a JSON schema defining valid workflow YAML structure,\n9\tso that malformed workflows are rejected at parse time with specific error messages.\n10\t\n11\t## Acceptance Criteria\n12\t\n13\t1. **Given** a workflow YAML file with valid `tasks` (each having `agent`, `scope`, `session`, `source_access`) and a valid `flow` array\n14\t   **When** validated against the JSON schema\n15\t   **Then** validation passes with no errors\n16\t   <!-- verification: test-provable -->\n17\t\n18\t2. **Given** a workflow YAML file missing the required `tasks` field\n19\t   **When** validated against the JSON schema\n20\t   **Then** validation fails with an error identifying the missing `tasks` field"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c54cfa66-957c-4f2c-a205-da1113d93a9b","uuid":"9b0ca0b8-5d40-4586-b03c-e1948187deea","timestamp":"2026-04-02T11:07:54.286Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/2-1-workflow-yaml-json-schema.md","content":"# Story 2.1: Workflow YAML JSON Schema\n\nStatus: ready-for-dev\n\n## Story\n\nAs a developer,\nI want a JSON schema defining valid workflow YAML structure,\nso that malformed workflows are rejected at parse time with specific error messages.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n1. **Given** a workflow YAML file with valid `tasks` (each having `agent`, `scope`, `session`, `source_access`) and a valid `flow` array\n   **When** validated against the JSON schema\n   **Then** validation passes with no errors\n   <!-- verification: test-provable -->\n\n2. **Given** a workflow YAML file missing the required `tasks` field\n   **When** validated against the JSON schema\n   **Then** validation fails with an error identifying the missing `tasks` field","numLines":20,"startLine":1,"totalLines":296}}}
