ort time regardless of usage. Negligible for CLI.\n\n**Coverage gaps:**\n- None. All metrics at 100% on the changed file. Overall project at 96.6%.\n\n**Architecture concerns:**\n- None. Schema file location (`src/schemas/`), validation utility location (`src/lib/`), and naming conventions all match the architecture-v2.md spec. `snake_case` YAML keys, `camelCase` functions, `PascalCase` types — all correct.\n\n**Items sent back for re-development:**\n- None. All HIGH and MEDIUM issues fixed. Story moved to `verifying`.\n\n## Token Report\n\n- Total tool calls: 18\n- By tool: Bash: 9, Read: 6, Edit: 3, Grep: 2, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs (top 3 by line count): `npx vitest run --coverage` full output (~80 lines), `git status --porcelain` combined (~30 lines), `npx tsc --noEmit` (~2 lines)\n- Files read: 8 unique, 8 total reads (no file read 3+ times)\n- Redundant operations: ran vitest coverage 3 times (initial check, post-edit verify, final coverage line grep) — could have been 2 if I'd grepped the first run output more carefully"}],"totalDurationMs":157567,"totalTokens":43281,"totalToolUseCount":31,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":352,"cache_read_input_tokens":41952,"output_tokens":976,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":352},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
