#4)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, keyword is \"enum\", path includes \"scope\".\n\n### AC5: Invalid session value fails validation\n**PASS** -- Test \"rejects invalid session value (AC #5)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, keyword is \"enum\", path includes \"session\".\n\n### AC6: loop: blocks validated (structural)\n**PASS** -- Test \"accepts a loop block in flow (AC #6)\" passes. Validates `{ loop: ['retry', 'verify'] }` is structurally accepted. Additional tests verify loop with empty array fails and loop with non-string items fails.\n\n### AC7: Missing agent field fails validation\n**PASS** -- Test \"rejects missing agent in task (AC #7)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, keyword is \"required\".\n\n### AC8: Schema file exists at src/schemas/workflow.schema.json\n**PASS** -- File exists at `src/schemas/workflow.schema.json` (92 lines). Confirmed via `ls` and `wc -l`.\n\n### AC9: Optional fields accepted when present, pass when absent\n**PASS** -- Test \"accepts optional fields when present and passes when absent (AC #9)\" passes. Tests `fullValidWorkflow()` (with prompt_template, input_contract, output_contract, source_access, max_budget_usd) and `minimalValidWorkflow()` (agent only). Both validate successfully.\n\n### AC10: All schema validation tests pass with 80%+ coverage\n**PASS** -- 28/28 tests pass. Coverage on `schema-validate.ts`: 100% statements, 100% branches, 100% functions, 100% lines. Exceeds 80% target.\n\n## Additional Evidence\n\n### TypeScript Exports\n`src/lib/schema-validate.ts` exports:\n- `interface ValidationError` (path, message, keyword)\n- `interface ValidationResult` (valid, errors)\n- `function validateAgainstSchema` (generic, reusable)\n- `function validateWorkflowSchema` (workflow-specific)\n\n### Error Structure\nTest \"returns errors with path, message, and keyword\" verifies every error object has `path` (string), `message` (string), and `keyword` (string) properties.\n\n### Schema Size\n`src/schemas/workflow.schema.json`: 92 lines (well under any reasonable limit).\n\n## Test Output (schema-validate.test.ts)\n\n```\n28 tests passed, 0 failed\n- validateWorkflowSchema > valid workflows (6 tests)\n- validateWorkflowSchema > missing required fields (3 tests)\n- validateWorkflowSchema > invalid enum values (2 tests)\n- validateWorkflowSchema > invalid types (2 tests)\n- validateWorkflowSchema > flow validation (4 tests)\n- validateWorkflowSchema > additional properties (2 tests)\n- validateWorkflowSchema > error structure (1 test)\n- validateWorkflowSchema > edge cases (3 tests)\n- validateAgainstSchema (5 tests)\n```\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":17,"oldLines":34,"newStart":17,"newLines":34,"lines":[" "," ## Acceptance Criteria Verification"," ","-### AC1: Valid workflow YAML passes validation","+## AC1: Valid workflow YAML passes validation"," **PASS** -- Test \"accepts a minimal valid workflow (AC #1)\" passes. Test \"accepts a full workflow with all optional fields (AC #9)\" passes. Both assert `result.valid === true` and `result.errors === []`."," ","-### AC2: Missing tasks field fails validation","+## AC2: Missing tasks field fails validation"," **PASS** -- Test \"rejects missing tasks field (AC #2)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, error message includes \"tasks\", keyword is \"required\"."," ","-### AC3: Missing flow field fails validation","+## AC3: Missing flow field fails validation"," **PASS** -- Test \"rejects missing flow field (AC #3)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, error message includes \"flow\", keyword is \"required\"."," ","-### AC4: Invalid scope value fails validation","+## AC4: Invalid scope value fails validation"," **PASS** -- Test \"rejects invalid scope value (AC #4)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, keyword is \"enum\", path includes \"scope\"."," ","-### AC5: Invalid session value fails validation","+## AC5: Invalid session value fails validation"," **PASS** -- Test \"rejects invalid session value (AC #5)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, keyword is \"enum\", path includes \"session\"."," ","-### AC6: loop: blocks validated (structural)","+## AC6: loop: blocks validated (structural)"," **PASS** -- Test \"accepts a loop block in flow (AC #6)\" passes. Validates `{ loop: ['retry', 'verify'] }` is structurally accepted. Additional tests verify loop with empty array fails and loop with non-string items fails."," ","-### AC7: Missing agent field fails validation","+## AC7: Missing agent field fails validation"," **PASS** -- Test \"rejects missing agent in task (AC #7)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, keyword is \"required\"."," ","-### AC8: Schema file exists at src/schemas/workflow.schema.json","+## AC8: Schema file exists at src/schemas/workflow.schema.json"," **PASS** -- File exists at `src/schemas/workflow.schema.json` (92 lines). Confirmed via `ls` and `wc -l`."," ","-### AC9: Optional fields accepted when present, pass when absent","+## AC9: Optional fields accepted when present, pass when absent"," **PASS** -- Test \"accepts optional fields when present and passes when absent (AC #9)\" passes. Tests `fullValidWorkflow()` (with prompt_template, input_contract, output_contract, source_access, max_budget_usd) and `minimalValidWorkflow()` (agent only). Both validate successfully."," ","-### AC10: All schema validation tests pass with 80%+ coverage","+## AC10: All schema validation tests pass with 80%+ coverage"," **PASS** -- 28/28 tests pass. Coverage on `schema-validate.ts`: 100% statements, 100% branches, 100% functions, 100% lines. Exceeds 80% target."," "," ## Additional Evidence"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":true}}
