{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01NzThcZHdPVrp4DAuxWtXhL","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Verification Proof: Story 2-1-workflow-yaml-json-schema\n2\t\n3\t**Story:** Workflow YAML JSON Schema\n4\t**Verified:** 2026-04-02\n5\t**Tier:** test-provable\n6\t**Verdict:** ALL_PASS (10/10 ACs)\n7\t\n8\t## Build & Test Summary\n9\t\n10\t| Check | Result |\n11\t|-------|--------|\n12\t| Build (`npm run build`) | PASS |\n13\t| Unit tests (`npm run test:unit`) | PASS (3580 passed) |\n14\t| Lint (`npm run lint`) | PASS (0 errors, 48 warnings) |\n15\t| Coverage (`schema-validate.ts`) | 100% statements, 100% branches, 100% functions, 100% lines |\n16\t| Schema-specific tests | 28/28 passed |\n17\t\n18\t## Acceptance Criteria Verification\n19\t\n20\t## AC1: Valid workflow YAML passes validation\n21\t**PASS** -- Test \"accepts a minimal valid workflow (AC #1)\" passes. Test \"accepts a full workflow with all optional fields (AC #9)\" passes. Both assert `result.valid === true` and `result.errors === []`.\n22\t\n23\t## AC2: Missing tasks field fails validation\n24\t**PASS** -- Test \"rejects missing tasks field (AC #2)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, error message includes \"tasks\", keyword is \"required\".\n25\t\n26\t## AC3: Missing flow field fails validation\n27\t**PASS** -- Test \"rejects missing flow field (AC #3)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, error message includes \"flow\", keyword is \"required\".\n28\t\n29\t## AC4: Invalid scope value fails validation\n30\t**PASS** -- Test \"rejects invalid scope value (AC #4)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, keyword is \"enum\", path includes \"scope\".\n31\t\n32\t## AC5: Invalid session value fails validation\n33\t**PASS** -- Test \"rejects invalid session value (AC #5)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, keyword is \"enum\", path includes \"session\".\n34\t\n35\t## AC6: loop: blocks validated (structural)\n36\t**PASS** -- Test \"accepts a loop block in flow (AC #6)\" passes. Validates `{ loop: ['retry', 'verify'] }` is structurally accepted. Additional tests verify loop with empty array fails and loop with non-string items fails.\n37\t\n38\t## AC7: Missing agent field fails validation\n39\t**PASS** -- Test \"rejects missing agent in task (AC #7)\" passes. Asserts `result.valid === false`, keyword is \"required\".\n40\t\n41\t## AC8: Schema file exists at src/schemas/workflow.schema.json\n42\t**PASS** -- File exists at `src/schemas/workflow.schema.json` (92 lines). Confirmed via `ls` and `wc -l`.\n43\t\n44\t## AC9: Optional fields accepted when present, pass when absent\n45\t**PASS** -- Test \"accepts optional fields when present and passes when absent (AC #9)\" passes. Tests `fullValidWorkflow()` (with prompt_template, input_contract, output_contract, source_access, max_budget_usd) and `minimalValidWorkflow()` (agent only). Both validate successfully.\n46\t\n47\t## AC10: All schema validation tests pass with 80%+ coverage\n48\t**PASS** -- 28/28 tests pass. Coverage on `schema-validate.ts`: 100% statements, 100% branches, 100% functions, 100% lines. Exceeds 80% target.\n49\t\n50\t## Additional Evidence\n51\t\n52\t### TypeScript Exports\n53\t`src/lib/schema-validate.ts` exports:\n54\t- `interface ValidationError` (path, message, keyword)\n55\t- `interface ValidationResult` (valid, errors)\n56\t- `function validateAgainstSchema` (generic, reusable)\n57\t- `function validateWorkflowSchema` (workflow-specific)\n58\t\n59\t### Error Structure\n60\tTest \"returns errors with path, message, and keyword\" verifies every error object has `path` (string), `message` (string), and `keyword` (string) properties.\n61\t\n62\t### Schema Size\n63\t`src/schemas/workflow.schema.json`: 92 lines (well under any reasonable limit).\n64\t\n65\t## Test Output (schema-validate.test.ts)\n66\t\n67\t```\n68\t28 tests passed, 0 failed\n69\t- validateWorkflowSchema > valid workflows (6 tests)\n70\t- validateWorkflowSchema > missing required fields (3 tests)\n71\t- validateWorkflowSchema > invalid enum values (2 tests)\n72\t- validateWorkflowSchema > invalid types (2 tests)\n73\t- validateWorkflowSchema > flow validation (4 tests)\n74\t- validateWorkflowSchema > additional properties (2 tests)\n75\t- validateWorkflowSchema > error structure (1 test)\n76\t- validateWorkflowSchema > edge cases (3 tests)\n77\t- validateAgainstSchema (5 tests)\n78\t```\n79\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01GSF2f4yiq81imWXCVyMGnW","session_id":"c54cfa66-957c-4f2c-a205-da1113d93a9b","uuid":"d18ac84f-4a2f-4021-bdfe-77f8e418d143","timestamp":"2026-04-02T11:19:54.299Z"}
