{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HGgu2hwH2pkEAxgDKSsJwF","type":"tool_result","content":"# Harness Cost Report\n\nTotal API-equivalent cost: $15.37\nTotal API calls: 119\nAverage cost per story: $6.91 (2 stories)\n\n## Cost by Token Type\n\n| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n|------|--------|------|------|---|\n| Cache reads | 6,796,708 | $1.50/MTok | $10.20 | 66% |\n| Cache writes | 160,732 | $18.75/MTok | $3.01 | 20% |\n| Output | 28,821 | $75/MTok | $2.16 | 14% |\n| Input | 127 | $15/MTok | $0.00 | 0% |\n\n## Cost by Phase\n\n| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n|-------|-------|------|---|\n| verify | 67 | $8.31 | 54.1% |\n| orchestrator | 11 | $2.28 | 14.8% |\n| create-story | 17 | $1.77 | 11.5% |\n| dev-story | 10 | $1.19 | 7.8% |\n| code-review | 9 | $1.04 | 6.8% |\n| retro | 5 | $0.78 | 5.0% |\n\n## Cost by Tool\n\n| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n|------|-------|------|---|\n| Bash | 34 | $3.91 | 25.4% |\n| Read | 30 | $3.57 | 23.2% |\n| Edit | 25 | $3.11 | 20.3% |\n| Agent | 14 | $2.12 | 13.8% |\n| Grep | 9 | $1.03 | 6.7% |\n| Skill | 2 | $0.75 | 4.9% |\n| Glob | 3 | $0.67 | 4.4% |\n| Write | 2 | $0.21 | 1.4% |\n\n## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n\n| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n|-------|-------|------|---|\n| 2-1-workflow-yaml-json-schema | 68 | $8.34 | 54.2% |\n| 1-3-workflow-state-module | 47 | $5.48 | 35.6% |\n| unknown | 4 | $1.56 | 10.1% |\n[OK] Report saved to /Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/cost-report.md","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_014qEcGGsz3MiamcyEZEG8mM","session_id":"c54cfa66-957c-4f2c-a205-da1113d93a9b","uuid":"710e8e59-086d-4c25-abc2-a66d2e6536cc","timestamp":"2026-04-02T11:22:36.231Z"}
